{"tid":2463047,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【睇片】New Yorker 訪新疆「再教育營」倖存者　製成 360° VR 動畫片","createTime":"2021-03-26T11:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T14:40:46.000Z","uid":41343,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6521d4bfb0961118388158da1e2e74bbe64f1252","tid":2463047,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:47:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newyorker.com/news/video-dept/reeducated-film-xinjiang-prisoners-china-virtual-reality\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fnews%2Fvideo-dept%2Freeducated-film-xinjiang-prisoners-china-virtual-reality&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWkzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=b52ad930\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newyorker.com/news/video-dept/reeducated-film-xinjiang-prisoners-china-virtual-reality</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/art/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-new-yorker-%E8%A8%AA%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86-%E5%86%8D%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E7%87%9F-%E5%80%96%E5%AD%98%E8%80%85-%E8%A3%BD%E6%88%90-360-vr-%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB%E7%89%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-new-yorker-%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586-%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E7%2587%259F-%25E5%2580%2596%25E5%25AD%2598%25E8%2580%2585-%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E6%2588%2590-360-vr-%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2595%25AB%25E7%2589%2587%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWkzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=e24c6560\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-new-yorker-%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586-%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E7%2587%259F-%25E5%2580%2596%25E5%25AD%2598%25E8%2580%2585-%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E6%2588%2590-360-vr-%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2595%25AB%25E7%2589%2587%2F&h=495afea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/art/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-new-yorker-%E8%A8%AA%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86-%E5%86%8D%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E7%87%9F-%E5%80%96%E5%AD%98%E8%80%85-%E8%A3%BD%E6%88%90-360-vr-%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB%E7%89%87/</a><br />\n<br />\n上星期，《New Yorker》雜誌重磅之作是一條足足 20 分鐘長片的 360&deg; VR 動畫&mdash;&mdash;《Reeducated》。他們幾位新疆「再教育營」倖存者的故事，把倖存者的口述歷史化成短片。短片根據三名哈薩克族男子的經寫成，並由插畫師 Matt Huynh 用筆墨再現大眾眼前。該片更獲得美國西南偏南電影節（South by Southwest, SXSW）虛擬影院類別、沉浸式報道評審特別嘉許的殊榮。（Special Jury Recognition for Immersive Journalism in the Virtual Cinema category at SXSW）<br />\n<br />\n多次到訪中亞的記者  Ben Mauk，聽過無數「再教育營」的傳聞。2019 年 12 月，他與導演 Sam Wolson、插畫師 Matt Huynh 深入哈薩克斯坦，與三名「再教育營」倖存者做訪問，然後製成 VR 動畫。Wolson 認為虛擬實境（VR）的沉浸式體驗，有助突出這些真人真事背後的情感。<br />\n<br />\n《Reeducated》片首稱，新疆位於中國境內，大部分人口信奉伊斯蘭教。2017 年春天，當局在新疆築起「秘密集中營」，拘留數以千計的土耳其及伊斯蘭人口。截至 2018 年，這些「再教育營」人口多達百萬。片中三人出生於新疆，曾移居哈薩克斯坦，其後返回中國：Amanzhan Seituly 是一名商人，抵達北京機場就被拘留；Orynbek Koksebek 回國奔喪；Erbaqyt Otarbai 則是一名中國煤礦公司的司機。他們互不相識，但都曾被囚禁於新疆塔城市的「秘密集中營」。<br />\n<br />\n全片黑白，描述三人在「再教育營」的經歷。他們每天一早起來說要唱紅歌，每餐吃蔬菜為主，一個月才有機會吃一次肉&mdash;&mdash;不知名的肉。他們每天上課十小時，又要抄書學寫漢字。有兩小時電視時間，但全都是習近平講話。課室黑板兩旁，各站一名持槍軍人。軍人周末又總愛到囚室翻箱倒籠，不知要查找甚麼⋯⋯"},{"pid":"8789d30f3a77b5edfd4efaaeee794b7932625ec5","tid":2463047,"uid":242537,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:05:05.000Z","msg":"1984<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/xinjiang_the_new_yorker_cap_screen-1520copy_NxJn6_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fxinjiang_the_new_yorker_cap_screen-1520copy_NxJn6_1200x0.png&h=6efaeeb2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a257de2be366598cf839c37885222358c47c50f2","tid":2463047,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12: